2020-07-27 Opto meta analysis

This is the first meta analysis done using the ephys database. As such it will be a broad survey of effects across various LN > ACR1 / CsChrimson experiments. The primary point of comparison will be the 1s odor stimulus, at high odor concentration - which is where the most prominent effects have been seen. Depending on how things go this analysis may expand to lower concentrations and alternate stimulus waveforms.
